data.description: Open concept floor plan with plenty of natural light. And a first floor Master bedroom and bathroom and Laundry room . This 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom home has new manufactured wood flooring though-out the lower level. Beautiful eatin kitchen with a view of the patio. The Garage is newly painted and insulated with cabinets and extra refrigerator included. The mechanical's were regularly serviced . This corner lot is close to the commuintiy club house and pool . Landscaped beauifully with full front porch to relax and enjoy easy living.  Close to grocery , restaurants, and shopping .  What else can you ask for ?See for yourself why this home will not last for long!
